POV: your lash artist who tells you not to get your fresh lash set wet and avoid sauna the first 24 hours is the same client who works out after the appt….. 😵‍💫😵‍💫😵‍💫

Honestly, guilty af. 
I do tell my clients to avoid getting them wet and in hot moist areas for the first 12 hours, but also who am I to judge because I too do it sometimes. 

I find it a myth of waiting 24 hours to be active because I find that it truly depends on the adhesive your artist uses in their station to fulfill the lash set. I normally tell my clients to atleast wait 8-12 hrs for the gurlys who are naturally oily and have early appointments in the day. 

Don’t be like me, working out and sweating right away after a lash set, but also… be like me to take care of your lashes by scheduling your fills appropriately if you’re an on-the-go gurly who has to fit in the gym every free time you can because you’re booked and busy 25/8. 

He he he. can’t blame yourself for wanting the gains 💪🏽😘

#fitness #workout #explorepage #whateva
